Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你們這些哥布林
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,居然敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,快使用治癒的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,慈愛的大地之母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,請治療她的傷口 治癒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,別亂揮 我上不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你去保護她們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這群傢伙就由我來解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 哥布林們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,明明已經施加了治癒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,卻沒有好轉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你們快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快…逃…
